    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="欢迎来到若泽数据，感谢大家对我们的支持"><a href="#欢迎来到若泽数据，感谢大家对我们的支持" class="headerlink" title="欢迎来到若泽数据，感谢大家对我们的支持"></a>欢迎来到若泽数据，感谢大家对我们的支持</h3><hr>
<h4 id="Spark"><a href="#Spark" class="headerlink" title="Spark"></a>Spark</h4><p>Run workloads 100x faster.</p>
<p>Apache Spark achieves high performance for both batch and streaming data, using a state-of-the-art DAG scheduler, a query optimizer, and a physical execution engine.</p>
<a id="more"></a>
<h4 id="Spark-web"><a href="#Spark-web" class="headerlink" title="Spark web"></a>Spark web</h4><p><a href="http://spark.apache.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">spark官网</a></p>
<h4 id="Spark-demo-code"><a href="#Spark-demo-code" class="headerlink" title="Spark demo code"></a>Spark demo code</h4><figure class="highlight scala"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">val</span> textFile = sc.textFile(<span class="string">"hdfs://..."</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">val</span> counts = textFile.flatMap(line =&gt; line.split(<span class="string">" "</span>))</span><br><span class="line">                 .map(word =&gt; (word, <span class="number">1</span>))</span><br><span class="line">                 .reduceByKey(_ + _)</span><br><span class="line">counts.saveAsTextFile(<span class="string">"hdfs://..."</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h4 id="Spark-img"><a href="#Spark-img" class="headerlink" title="Spark img"></a>Spark img</h4><p><img src="/2015/07/11/spark/logistic-regression.png" alt></p>
<ul>
<li>spark core</li>
<li>spark streaming</li>
<li>spark sql </li>
</ul>
]]></content>
